data.description: 412 Morning Mist Dr in Upscale Morning Lake subdivision in Moore. Beautiful custom built 4 bed 3.5 bath home with bonus room and office, every upgrade the builder could install was done to this home with no expense spared. Leaded glass door with transom window greets you and leads you on to beautiful hardwood floors, tall ceilings and abundance of quality moldings to showcase what a builder can do when asked to build it like its for himself. Oversized formal dining room  built to take the largest of tables, beautiful hardwood floor, trey ceiling, double crown and chair moldings, wainscoting and lots of natural light. Den/office or breakfast room continues with hardwood floors, crown & chair molding and wainscoting, making for a great semi private location for so many things. Gourmet kitchen has granite counters, abundance of hardwood cabinets, recessed lighting and upscale stainless steel appliances, all with granite breakfast bar. Living room has two story cathedral ceiling with fan, gas log fireplace and dual Palladian windows for ample light. Great room continues with hardwood floors, another gas log fireplace, 2 story ceiling with fan, recessed lighting and built in bookshelves. Master suite on main floor has room for large furniture, trey ceiling, crown molding and ceiling fan. Master bath has oversized jacuzzi tub with tiled backsplash and floor, dual sink vanity with oil brushed lighting fixtures. Walk in shower and huge walk in closet. Upstairs landing is open and spacious. Spare bedrooms all have ceiling fans, one has walk in closet, other has dual closets. Two full bathrooms upstairs to accommodate larger families. Bonus room is huge with cathedral ceiling with fan and closet so it could be used for 5th bedroom if desired. Screened porch out back has private view of wooded yard with lots of level space. Home comes complete with alarm, irrigation, surround sound enabled and central vacuum systems. Come see it today.
